: **_(Front-panel LEDs)_**

_(Power light)_:
: <select name="LED_POWER"><?php opts([1=>'On',0=>'Off'], $val('LED_POWER','1')); ?></select>

_(Network / LAN light)_:
: <input type="color" name="LED_LAN" value="<?=col($cfg,'LED_LAN','#0064ff')?>">

_(Disk light &mdash; healthy)_:
: <input type="color" name="LED_DISK_OK" value="<?=col($cfg,'LED_DISK_OK','#00ff00')?>">

_(Disk light &mdash; warning)_:
